    <bioghist encodinganalog="MARC 545"> 
      <p>Originally sent as recruiting tools to the College of Architecture,
        Art, and Planning.</p> 
    </bioghist> 
    <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520"> 
      <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head> 
      <p>Brochures from architectural firms showcasing their work. Firms
        include Amenta/Emma, Bowie Gridley Architects, Burt Hill Kosar Rittelmann
        Associates, The Design Alliance, EYP Mission Critical Facilities, Inc.,
        Hellmuth, Obata + Kassabaum, Hillier Architecture, HOLT Architects, Mancini
        Duffy, McCall Design Group, Michael Graves Architects, Odell, Perkins Eastman
        Architects, Simon Martin Vegue Winkelstein Moris.</p> 
      <p>Also, "A Proposal for a branch bank of The City National Bank and Trust Company,
        Gloversville, New York," Edgar Tafel Architect, n.d.; "Schematic Presentation for
        Atlantic City Performing Arts Center," Taliesin Associated Architects of the Frank
        Lloyd Wright Foundation, William Wesley Peters, Architect, 1975.</p>
    </scopecontent> 
